A thief has been caught on camera stealing a female bag from Transcorp Hilton Hotel, Abuja. Former Director General, Bureau of Public Reforms, Dr Joe Abah has asked Nigerians to help him identify a man that stole his PA’s handbag at the Benue Hall of the Transcorp Hilton in Abuja. Abah shared CCTV footage showing the man lifting the bag from where it was kept. He wrote, ”This guy stole my P.A.’s handbag from the Benue Hall of Transcorp Hilton Abuja this morning. Any information leading to his arrest will be greatly appreciated and rewarded.” Watch video below: This guy stole my P.A.’s handbag from the Benue Hall of Transcorp Hilton Abuja this morning. Any information leading to his arrest will be greatly appreciated and rewarded. Cc. ⁦@PoliceNG_CRU⁩ ⁦@PoliceNG⁩ pic.twitter.com/aHilHUZlBT Source: tori.ng